This directory contains code for software benchmark of Palm Beach
packet processing.

The following codes are released for Shan to benchmark:
pb_dyn.c	Palm Beach packet processing (Dynamic table scheduling)
pb_fifo.c	Palm Beach packet processing (FIFO scheduling from Pierre)


pb.c		Palm Beach packet processing benchmark (developing version)

Tools to generate test data:
ipEncap.c	IP encapsulation of SPTS
ipMux.c		Muxing several IP ecnapsulated SPTS into an MPTS


